            "description": "<div class=\"article-body\">\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">港元拆息向上，與樓按相關的1個月拆息報3.51464厘，終止五連跌，升1.779基點。</p>\n<a class=\"image-lightbox\" data-caption=\"資料圖片\" data-fancybox=\"gallery-mainpost\" href=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/1200x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/09/20250917_PO_source_bp_policy-address_19.jpg.webp\">\n<img alt=\"資料圖片\" src=\"https://image.bastillepost.com/1200x/wp-content/uploads/hongkong/2025/09/20250917_PO_source_bp_policy-address_19.jpg.webp\"/>\n<p class=\"caption font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"14\">資料圖片</p>\n</a>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">反映銀行資金成本的3個月拆息報3.58905厘，升4.881基點。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">隔夜息報3.62036厘，升2.036基點；1周拆息升4.761基點，報3.54702厘。</p>\n\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">長息方面，6個月拆息升2.774基點，報3.44024厘，1年期則無升跌，報3.38619厘。</p>\n</div>",
