            "title": "即月期指開跌82點     高水13點",
            "description": "<div class=\"article-body\">\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">即月期指報27300，跌82點或0.3%，高水13點。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">科指期貨報6697，跌17點或0.25% ， 高水14點。</p>\n<p class=\"font-size-scaler-control\" data-font=\"16\">國指期貨報9727，跌36點,0.37%，高水3點。</p>\n</div>",
            "link": "https://www.bastillepost.com/hongkong/article/15314604-%e5%8d%b3%e6%9c%88%e6%9c%9f%e6%8c%87%e9%96%8b%e8%b7%8c82%e9%bb%9e-%e9%ab%98%e6%b0%b413%e9%bb%9e",
